data.description: Ranch home with Lakes of Four Seasons Private Security Force.Totally rehabbed home within the last 4 to 5 years.  Everything updated.  New roof, heat, hot water heater, water softener, kitchen appliances, two sump pumps, two skylights, kitchen cabinets, quartz kitchen counters tops. All New Windows. New bathrooms, one with jetted tub, both with a Walk in Shower.  Crown Molding, Heated Garage. Trex decking and so much more!Four Lakes, Swimming, Boating, 18 Hole Championship Golf Course and Pro Shop, Restaurants, Beaches, Tennis Courts, Swimming Pool, Animal Park, Playgrounds and so many more amenities.
